{"type":"after","callId":"call@37","endTime":177412.991,"result":{"matches":false,"received":{"s":"InHandKnow your real take-homeSalaryOffer comparisonLog inSign upCalculatorSalary calculatorEnter guaranteed fixed pay and optional variable pay. The summary shows what is dependable every month versus an illustrative view if variable is included, plus regime-aware TDS tied to your Old / New regime selection.Salary detailsEnter total CTC to fill fixed pay and clear variable; add variable if part of your package—or edit fixed/variable directly so totals stay in sync.ResetTax regimeOld regimeSlabs + rebates (no 80C/HRA in this quick calc)New regimeLower slabs; standard deduction only hereIn-hand and TDS estimates in the summary follow this regime (Old vs New slabs).Total package (CTC)Annual cash compensation (fixed + variable). Updating this sets fixed to the full amount and clears variable until you add it.Annual CTC₹Fixed ₹18,00,000 + variable ₹0 = ₹18,00,000Fixed payCore salary you can treat as dependable monthly cash (before statutory deductions and TDS).Annual fixed pay₹Variable payVariable CTC, performance bonus, or incentives—often not paid every month and not guaranteed. We still spread it over 12 months for an \"illustrative\" in-hand next to your fixed-only number.Annual variable pay (expected)₹Standard monthly deductionsProfessional tax₹Employee PF₹Employer PF (monthly)₹Does not reduce in-hand; shown in the composition chart as part of your package.LabelMonthly₹Add deductionPremiumUnlock detailed salary breakdownGet a more precise read on your compensation with component-level breakup and deeper payroll insights—when you are ready to go further.View component-level breakup and allowances in contextUnderstand deductions and cash path with richer detailConnect this salary to premium planning when you upgradeUnlock PremiumCompare Free & Premium plansSummaryEstimated in-handNew regimeGuaranteed figures use fixed pay only—what you can typically count on each month. Illustrative numbers add variable pay spread over 12 months; they are a broader estimate only (variable may be lumpy, conditional, or not guaranteed).Guaranteed monthly in-handFixed pay only — dependable baseline₹1,35,433Illustrative monthly in-handIncluding variable, averaged per month₹1,35,433Guaranteed annual in-handFixed pay basis, ×12₹16,25,196Illustrative annual in-handIncluding variable, full year view₹16,25,196Regime-aware TDS estimateIncome tax below follows the New regime slabs used in this calculator (standard deduction; no 80C/HRA in this quick view). Same regime applies to both guaranteed and illustrative views—only the gross base changes when variable is included.Monthly tax (fixed gross)₹12,567Annual (fixed)₹1,50,800Effective rate on gross:Fixed 8.4%Live estimateUpdates as you edit fixed, variable, deductions, or regime.New regime · FY 2025-26AY 2026-27 · resident slabs = in-app TDS basisNew regime — seven concessional slabs; no separate deduction stack in this model beyond std. deduction.Slab (₹/yr)RateUp to ₹4,00,000Nil₹4,00,001 – ₹8,00,0005%₹8,00,001 – ₹12,00,00010%₹12,00,001 – ₹16,00,00015%₹16,00,001 – ₹20,00,00020%₹20,00,001 – ₹24,00,00025%Above ₹24,00,00030%FY 2025-26 reference. In-hand and tax above follow these slabs after ₹75,000 standard deduction.Slab rates shown are before cess; your summary applies 4% cess and eligible rebate.Taxable: cash minus std. deduction ₹75,000. · TDS: slabs + 4% cess; 87A if below ₹12,00,000.Indicative — not tax advice.Package compositionUses the same monthly basis as your illustrative in-hand (fixed + variable gross + employer PF). Visual split only—not a payslip.Take-homeof monthly viz. total89%Deductions + taxof monthly viz. total10%Employer PFin package (viz. total)1%Offer comparisonGot two offers? See which one actually pays more.Stop guessing. Paste both CTCs—see in-hand, tax, and first-year value side by side before the call.HRA / mo₹21.6KPF (employee)11.2%Gratuity (yr)₹4.3LVariable weight16.8%Sample comparison · not your dataOffer AUnicorn₹38 LPAOffer BMNC India₹36 LPAIn-hand / mo₹2,12,800₹2,05,400Est. tax / mo₹61.0K₹57.3K1st year value₹28.4L₹27.1LLensESOP notional incl. · +₹1.3LJoining bonus₹1.9LESOP (1Y notional)₹2.4LTDS effective21.7%Tax regimeOldPremium unlocks live offer comparison.Compare My OffersPremium planningWhat you can do with this salaryForecasts, debt fit, and monthly allocation build on your in-hand estimate—available on Premium when you are ready.PremiumWealth ForecastSee how your salary can turn into savings and net worth over the next few years.Go PremiumPremiumEMI AnalyzerCheck what EMI is realistically affordable based on your actual in-hand salary.Go PremiumPremiumMonthly PlannerTurn your salary into a realistic monthly spending and savings plan.Go PremiumInHandKnow your real take-homeSalary intelligence for Indian employees—in-hand clarity, breakups, tax context, and decisions without the fluff.ProductCalculatorPricingForecastCompareLegalPrivacyTermsSecurityWhy InHandReal take-home clarity—not a generic CTC guessEvery figure below matches what the app actually helps you do: line-level salary math, regime choice, and privacy without bank linking.Full pay breakupPF, deductions, professional tax, and income-tax estimates on your CTC—so you see estimated monthly in-hand, not just the package headline.Old vs new regimeModel Old and New tax treatment in the same flow. Handy for comparing which structure you’re using—not a full ITR filing wizard.Private by designEnter CTC and assumptions yourself—no bank linking or payroll import. On premium, you can keep a saved list on this device to jump between scenarios without retyping everything. 256-BIT SSL ISO CERTIFIED GDPR COMPLIANT© 2026 InHand. All rights reserved."}},"afterSnapshot":"after@call@37"}
